          "reviewBody": "Mahamaya balika inter college is not just the school where student came, study  and go out but it is more than that....\nIt teaches the students how to develop holistically .students of here are really very creative without the facility of internet bstudents the guidance and support of teachers.\nIf we talk about teachers, they are really very supportive, caring, understanding and really very knowledgeable.\nPrincipal (Mrs.Pratiba chaudhary) is very good and fully devoted for the wellfare of students.\nIts main and very attractive feature is its infrastructure it was really very fabulous. now we came at its hostel's facility it is well provided with 24 hours electricity, water five time meal a day with different recipes, first aid facility and it is fully cleaned and maintained.\nIt is also well guarded and its provide proper security to all the students\n_A honest review by the pass out student of school",
